SALESFORCE RELEASE NOTES
Get More Trust Layer Audit Dashboards and Reports

We’re adding new pre-built dashboards and reports in Data Cloud to help you monitor and verify the Einstein Trust Layer metrics. Now, you can easily see and verify how data masking works in prompts and responses. Explore content safety issues such as toxicity in the generated responses.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions with an Einstein for Sales, Einstein for Platform, or Einstein for Service add-on.

When: The new reports and dashboards will be available starting mid-July 2024.

Who: Anyone who has access to reports and dashboards can use this feature.

How: The latest reports and dashboards are available after you turn on the Einstein Generative AI Data Collection and Storage feature in the Einstein Generative AI Setup.

If you previously installed the Einstein Generative AI and Feedback Data report package, you can now uninstall it. The package is no longer necessary for accessing the audit and feedback reports and dashboards.

This update includes the Einstein Trust Layer dashboard, which is dynamic. Because it’s a dynamic dashboard, it counts toward your total number of available dynamic dashboards.
